Class OtherUserProfile.Read

  • java.lang.Object
      • gosuninjas.koinbox.OtherUser.OtherUserProfile.Read
  • Enclosing class:
    OtherUserProfile

    public class OtherUserProfile.Read
extends
    This function reads data from the resulting JSONArray and JSONObject above and saves information into one dimensional array: result_array. The first 5 values are name, age, university, home_city and away_city. The following values are interests, in particularly type and description for each interest. Textviews are generated to show the values in the array at appropriate positions on the phone
